UID:EmydXBb5CFD9iFnmeCwCt
SUMMARY:Bollywood & Bhangra Dance
DTSTAMP:20260625T012300Z
DTSTART:20260624T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Get ready to move\, sweat\, and dance in this fitness-based dan
	ce class inspired by the vibrant rhythms of Bollywood and the powerful bea
	ts of Bhangra. Designed for all ages\, abilities\, and experience levels\,
	 this class welcomes everyone — whether you’re stepping onto the dance flo
	or for the first time or already love to dance. \n  \n  \n \n\nhttps://www
	.levyparkhouston.org/events/bollywood-bhangra-dance-2-2-4-2/2026-06-24/\n\
	nFrom Levy Park Houston
URL:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/bollywood-bhangra-dance-2-2-4-2/
	2026-06-24/
LOCATION:Levy Park (Event Pavilion)\, TX
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:levy-park-houston
CATEGORIES:Levy Park Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
IMAGE;VALUE=URI;DISPLAY=BADGE;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.levyparkhousto
 n.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/2026-06.24_Web-Graphic.jpg
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/wp-content/upload
 s/2026/05/2026-06.24_Web-Graphic.jpg
UID:zML8AiBZw6t8wtCctexmY
SUMMARY:Free Watch Party: Czechia vs. Mexico
DTSTAMP:20260625T012300Z
DTSTART:20260624T183000Z
DESCRIPTION:Two proud soccer nations with everything to play for. Czechia b
	rings the grit and heart of Eastern Europe while Mexico fights for glory o
	n home turf. This group stage showdown is going to be electric\, so come p
	ick a side and make some noise! \nFestival gates open at 6:30 p.m. to the 
	sounds of DJ Cris. Kickoff is at 8:00 p.m. Admission is free! \nFood and B
	everage Concessions: Enjoy a variety of festival food fare\, beer and wine
	\, and non-alcoholic beverages from Coca-Cola. Visit Smalls Sliders for bu
	rgers\, fries\, and shakes and cool down with Frios Gourmet Pops. Stop by 
	Hearsay’s festival tent for a cold beer or beer bucket or grab a michelada
	\, wine\, or beer from Gaspacho’s festival tent. Non-alcoholic drinks from
	 Coca-Cola as well as pre-packaged snacks can be purchased at the Communit
	y Partner Concessions Booth\, proceeds benefiting Levy Park and the event’
	s community partners. \nFace Painting & Henna Art: Get into the tournament
	 spirit with face and body art from Butterfly Faces by Shondra Macklin and
	 Henna Station & Glitter Bar \nCommunity Partners and Volunteers: Levy Par
	k is representing a wide array of non-profit park partners for this event.
	 All sales generated at the Community Partner Concessions booth will suppo
	rt Levy Park’s maintenance and operation. Email us to learn more about vol
	unteer opportunities. \nMerchandise: Event merchandise celebrating Houston
	\, Levy Park\, and the global soccer tournament will also be available for
	 purchase. \nArt Installations and Photo Opportunities: Commemorate the ex
	perience with a photo tour of the park\, including life-sized soccer-theme
	d photo backdrops and a tournament bracket. Visit our soccer ball music bo
	x and turn the crank for festive sounds. \nFestival Guidelines: \nVISITORS
	 MUST COMPLY WITH DIRECTIONS FROM PARK PERSONNEL\, OR THEY WILL BE ASKED T
	O LEAVE THE PARK. PARENTS ARE RESPONSIBLE FOR THEIR CHILDREN’S SAFETY IN T
	HE PARK. \nCHAIRS AND SEATING: No outside furniture. Blankets may be broug
	ht into the Festival site for the designated blanket seating area. All oth
	er furniture is available on a first-come\, first-served basis. \nSTROLLER
	S & WAGONS: Oversized strollers and wagons may need to be parked in a desi
	gnated area during the festival. All visitors must comply with park person
	nel regarding stroller and wagon parking. \nFOOD AND BEVERAGES: Guests are
	 permitted to enter with one factory-sealed bottle of water. Outside food 
	and drinks are prohibited (exceptions will be made for baby food and neces
	sary medical dietary food items). A variety of food\, non-alcoholic drinks
	\, beer\, and wine will be available for purchase from Festival concession
	aires. \nRE-ENTRY: If you leave the Festival site\, you will be re-screene
	d before re-entry. \nTHE FOLLOWING ARE PROHIBITED: \n\nSmoking or Vaping\n
	Umbrellas\nDrug Use\nKites and Drones\nRecreational Motorized Vehicles\nGu
	ns\, knives\, any weaponry\nSoliciting\nBikes\, scooters\, rollerblades\, 
	and roller skates\n\nhttps://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/czechia-mexico
	/\n\nFrom Levy Park Houston
URL:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/czechia-mexico/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:levy-park-houston
CATEGORIES:Levy Park Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT5H
END:VEVENT
